      "description": "CFD-predicted hydraulic performance (pressure head at 5 flow-speed operating points) compared against FDA published experimental data. Mean absolute error 3.2%; all points within experimental uncertainty band. Validation conducted at nominal operating conditions; no low-shear recirculation regime specifically exercised."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/rh-index-relative-hemolysis-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) comparison against bench measurements",
      "description": "Predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) values converted to RH index and compared against in-vitro bench measurements at 3 operating points. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all tested conditions. Validation dataset spans moderate-to-high shear operating points only; low-shear recirculation zone hemolysis contribution not represented in the experimental test matrix."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/mesh-independence-study",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh independence study — hemolysis QoI convergence",
      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (4.2M, 8.7M, 16.1M cells) assessed. GCI for NIH QoI < 2.1% between medium and fine meshes. Fine mesh selected for all production runs."
    }
  ],
